name: The Dark Side
description:
We always hide and ignore the dark side of our soul , we beat that part of us to death but we forget that we need that part to live, to be passionate, dangerous and reckless in life sometimes. You’re not complete without that part.
God is waiting for you in peace ,somewhere between the angels and the demons of your soul . So be you , be perfect.
2721*2721 pixels 
Both handmade and digital
